Exhibit #237 of how Congress is broken. We worked all year to pass @SenatorHeitkamp's bill to fight the epidemic of missing and murdered Native women and girls. We convinced all 100 Senators! Now it's on life support because of 1 retiring Congressman?

Pass #SavannasAct. https://twitter.com/jbendery/status/1075015137269039104 QT @jbendery Good morning. A single GOP congressman is blocking a bill to help abused Native women. It sailed through the Senate + was on track to pass the House. It's on the verge of expiring if he doesn't let it go.

@RepGoodlatte won't say why he's doing this. https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/native-women-abused-bill-bob-goodlatte_us_5c17eafce4b0b1ea387f584b?cnp
